RACE.FOOTNOTES: MOTORIZED set the early pace then maintained a good distance between other foe. STAY BY THE BEACH moved in early on was slightly off pace, showed a little rally to separate from the rest of the pack. WHISPER'S MARK broke a little late out of the gate then took the corner in the five path with a huge outside rally to reach the podium. RACE.FOOTNOTES: WHY FOR set the early pace snuck down to the rail while maintaining the position on the rail dueled LA DELHOMME'S SHOW down the stretch and held out for the win by sneaking a length and a quarter at the last few jumps. LA DELHOMME'S SHOW ran off pace dueled BURNINGDAYLIGHT in the first half of the race then coming onto the stretch dueled WHY FOR for the remainder of the race. BURNINGDAYLIGHT ran in the two path maintained an even pace throughout the race. REALLY A STORM had a slow mild gain in pace throughout the race in the two path after the three hundred yards. SHE'S ALL ATTITUDE ran on the rail but didn't kick until mid stretch. SNOOZY SUZY ran in the three path was pushed out by MOONLIT FOREST. MOONLIT FOREST ran on the rail blew the turn and pushed out foe. SUMMER PUDDING had a mild gain coming around the corner but lost interest on the stretch. Race was Hand Times.
